{"tid":983677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"龍床曝光: 90呎客廳全屋5步行完 貼牆沖涼轉唔到身","createTime":"2019-01-16T07:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T10:19:20.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eabe9b9ac621e2bed132ce6d31842f171bfa1d87","tid":983677,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"由佳源國際控股及陞域集團合作的屯門新盤菁雋，以全港最細單位面積成為焦點，惟發展商不願開放128呎的示範單位，使當時全港傳媒都扭盡六壬去感受龍床盤如何生活。<br />\n<br />\n由內房佳源和舖王鄧成波旗下之陞域集團合作竟然劏出一梯廿九伙奇則，單位設計以大學學生宿舍作參考，發展商指，「就算紫禁城咁大，皇帝瞓覺嗰陣都係得張龍床」，龍床比喻備受全城爭議。<br />\n<br />\n不要以為128呎那麼細就沒有廚房，電磁爐和鋅盤緊貼窗戶，而單位內只有兩個單邊窗，分別在客廳和浴室。整個浴室也只有四個階磚大。除此之外，少於90呎的客廳附送組合櫃，集雪櫃、飯桌及儲物於一身。<br />\n<br />\n想知128呎劏房單位到底有幾細？馬上去片！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190115/2_649696_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190115%2F2_649696_0&d=ll1HIowsE26aSNlWinny48P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=e944fcf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20190115%2F2_649696_0&h=cefb6821\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20190115/2_649696_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d1305f0f2d2369af7e67535e3441204f96dde7","tid":983677,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:34:34.000Z","msg":"好撚正 <br />\n0尺笑128尺"},{"pid":"ee27a010d058f8cd7b61fac775e9a9e0d942b62d","tid":983677,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c23b28e937f1c9eddf477ec1f637ea1e578e76ab","tid":983677,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a1d1305f0f2d2369af7e67535e3441204f96dde7","tid":983677,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:34:34.000Z","msg":"好撚正 <